ng antioxidant-rich argan oil, Vitamins A and E and red algae for optimal hydration and conditioning.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"row-fluid\">\r\n					\r\n					<div class=\"span4\">\r\n						<h4>Style</h4>\r\n						<p>Extend and enhance the life of every style with argan oil-infused products that prep and protect hair from hot tools and set the stage for optimal styling.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"span4\">\r\n						<h4>Scalp Treatments</h4>\r\n						<p>Restore scalp imbalances for dry or oily scalps the treatments that will relieve irritation and revitalize hair.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"span4\">\r\n						<h4>Body</h4>\r\n						<p>A full line of products to nourish and revive the skin with antioxidants and oils that will leave the skin feeling luxuriously smooth and looking radiant. </p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n'),(803,110,'_products_2_product_info','field_52c35cae3957e'),(804,110,'products','3'),(805,110,'_products','field_52c35c533957b'),(806,110,'color_content','<p>We only treat your hair with products that maintain and strengthen the integrity of your hair. That\'s why we\'ve chosen premium color lines that will allow you to achieve the long-lasting look you want without damaging your hair. Each of the color lines we carry is free of harsh chemicals and odors that can  compromising the health of your hair. When you get your hair colored at Champu Salon you can be assured you\'ll leave with strong, healthy and beautiful hair. </p>'),(807,110,'_color_content','field_5302a62f83e20'),(808,110,'color_products_0_product_name','Inoa'),(809,110,'_color_products_0_product_name','field_5302a64283e22'),(810,110,'color_products_0_product_logo','103'),(811,110,'_color_products_0_product_logo','field_5302a64283e23'),(812,110,'color_products_0_unique_id','inoa'),(813,110,'_color_products_0_unique_id','field_5302a64283e24'),(814,110,'color_products_0_product_info','<img src=\"http://champusalonjh.com/wp-content/upload