ther nutrients.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"span4\">\r\n						<h4>Hydrate</h4>\r\n						<p>Leaves hair soft shiny and more manageable. Infused with replenishing nutrients including antioxidant-rich argan oil, Vitamins A and E and red algae for optimal hydration and conditioning.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"row-fluid\">\r\n					\r\n					<div class=\"span4\">\r\n						<h4>Style</h4>\r\n						<p>Extend and enhance the life of every style with argan oil-infused products that prep and protect hair from hot tools and set the stage for optimal styling.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"span4\">\r\n						<h4>Scalp Treatments</h4>\r\n						<p>Restore scalp imbalances for dry or oily scalps the treatments that will relieve irritation and revitalize hair.</p>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"span4\">\r\n						<h4>Body</h4>\r\n						<p>A full line of products to nourish and revive the skin with antioxidants and oils that will leave the skin feeling luxuriously smooth and looking radiant. </p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n'),(1051,120,'_products_2_product_info','field_52c35cae3957e'),(1052,120,'products','3'),(1053,120,'_products','field_52c35c533957b'),(1054,120,'color_content','<p>We only treat your hair with products that maintain and strengthen the integrity of your hair. That\'s why we\'ve chosen premium color lines that will allow you to achieve the long-lasting look you want without damaging your hair. Each of the color lines we carry is free of harsh chemicals and odors that can  compromising the health of your hair. When you get your hair colored at Champu Salon you can be assured you\'ll leave with strong, healthy and beautiful hair. </p>'),(1055,120,'_color_content','field_5302a62f83e20'),(1056,120,'color_products_0_product_name','Inoa'),(1057,120,'_color_products_0_product_name','field_5302a64283e22'),(1058,120,'color_products_0_product_logo','111'),(1059,120,'_color_products_0_product_logo','field_5302a64283e23'),(1060,120,'color_products_0_unique_id','inoa'),(1061,120,'_color_products_0_unique_id','field_5302a64283e24'),(1062,120,'color_products_0_product_info','<img src=\"http://champusalonjh.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/INOA-product-shot.jpg\" style=\"width: 170px; float:right; margin-left: 10px;\"/>\r\n<p>Known to hair industry professionals as the caviar of color lines, INOA\'s Oil Delivery System technology uses the power of oil to truly maximize coloring action with a minimum concentration of  damaging agents, leaving hair smoother, softer and shinier than before coloration. And, developed to deliver uniform and exact results, INOA optimizes scalp comfort with an ammonia-free and odorless formulation. With 6 weeks of intense hydration and nutrition delivered to your hair post-color, you can feel great about leaving the salon with long-lasting INOA color and healthier hair.  </p>\r\n<p>Learn more about <a href=\"http://www.inoa-us.com/\" target=\"_blank\">INOA</a></p>'),(1063,120,'_color_products_0_product_info','field_5302a64283e25'),(1064,120,'color_products_1_product_name','Pravana Chromasilk'),(1065,120,'_color_products_1_product_name','field_5302a64283e22'),(1066,120,'color_products_1_product_logo','113'),(1067,120,'_color_products_1_product_logo','field_5302a64283e23'),(1068,120,'color_products_1_unique_id','pravana'),(1069,120,'_color_products_1_unique_id','field_5302a64283e24'),(1070,120,'color_products_1_product_info','<img src=\"http://champusalonjh.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/pravana_chromasilk.jpg\" style=\"float:right; margin-left: 10px;\">\r\n<p>Pravana’s premium and versatile ChromaSilk color line provides top performance and color vibrancy. With a full range of 101 permanent, low-ammonia colors that employ a proprietary blend of keratin amino acids and pure silk protein, Pravana ChromaSilk colors provide lasting protection, added strength, and unparalleled shine. Let us help you achieve your ideal hair color with Pravana ChromaSilk, or get creative with the stunning colors and shades offered by ChromaSilk Vivids or Pastels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Learn more about <a href=\"http://www.pravana.com/products/chromasilk_haircolor.html\" target=\"_blank\">ChromaSilk</a>, <a href=\"http://www.pravana.com/products/chromasilk_pastels.htm\" target=\"_blank\">ChromaSilk Pastels</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.pravana.com/products/chromasilk_vivids.html\" target=\"_blank\">ChromaSilk Vivids</a>.</p>'),(1071,120,'_color_products_1_product_info','field_5302a64283e25'),(1072,120,'color_products_2_product_name','Redken Shades EQ'),(1073,120,'_color_products_2_product_name','field_5302a64283e22'),(1074,120,'color_products_2_product_logo','118'),(1075,120,'_color_products_2_product_logo','field_5302a64283e23'),(1076,120,'color_products_2_unique_id','redken'),(1077,120,'_color_products_2_unique_id','field_5302a64283e24'),(1078,120,'color_products_2_product_info','<img src=\"http://champusalonjh.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/redken-product-shot.jpg\" style=\"float:right; margin-left: 10px;\"/>\r\n<p>Redken Shades EQ is a demi-permanent haircolor that enriches natural color, refreshes faded haircolor and tones or corrects color without lightening your hair. This line is the perfect choice for achieving exceptional color with depth, dimension, shine and style without altering the natural pigment of your hair. The Shades EQ line will maximize your hair\'s potential by adding shine and condition to your natural or color-treated hair. </p>'),(1079,120,'_color_products_2_product_info','field_5302a64283e25'),(1080,120,'color_products','3'),(1081,120,'_color_products','field_5302a64283e21'),(1082,27,'color_products_2_product_name','DIA Richesse & DIA Light'),(1083,27,'_color_products_2_product_name','field_5302a64283e22'),(1084,27,'color_products_2_product_logo','128'),(1085,27,'_color_products_2_product_logo','field_5302a64283e23'),(1086,27,'color_products_2_unique_id','dia'),(1087,27,'_color_products_2_unique_id','field_5302a64283e24'),(1088,27,'co