INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2013-04-29 19:13:58','2013-04-29 19:13:58','<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 18px; \">1160 Alpine Lane, Suite 1G &bull; Jackson, Wyoming 83001 &bull; (307) 739-4646</p>\r\n	<div class=\"row-fluid\" style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px dashed #ebebeb; padding: 40px 0 50px 0;\">\r\n		<div class=\"span4 offset2\">\r\n	\r\n		<h3>HAIR</h3>\r\n		<p>Women\'s Cut.......$45.00 & up</p>\r\n		<p>Men\'s Cut.......$25.00 & up</p>\r\n		<p>Kid\'s Cut.......$20.00 & up</p>\r\n		<p>Shampoo & Blow dry.......$35.00 & up</p>\r\n	\r\n		<h3>NAILS</h3>\r\n		<p>Manicure.......$30.00</p>\r\n		\r\n		<p>Pedicure.......$65.00</p>\r\n	\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"span4\">\r\n		<h3>COLOR</h3>\r\n		<p>One Process.......$55.00 & up</p>\r\n		<p>Full Foil.......$105.00 & up</p>\r\n		<p>Partial Foil.......$85.00 & up</p>\r\n		<p>Lash Tint.......$25.00</p>\r\n		<p>Brow Tint.......$20.00</p>\r\n		<h3>WAXING</h3>\r\n		<p>Brows/lip/chin.......$15.00 each</p>\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>','Champu Salon','','draft','open','closed','','under-constructio','','','2014-01-02 19:13:18','2014-01-02 19:13:18','',0,'http://champusalonjh.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(15,1,'2013-10-21 19:35:28','2013-10-21 19:35:28','','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2014-01-02 19:18:30','2014-01-02 19:18:30','',0,'http://champusalonjh.com/?page_id=15',0,'page','',0),(18,1,'2013-10-24 23:07:06','2013-10-24 23:07:06','<h2>About</h2>\r\n<p>Located in Jackson, Wyoming, Champu Salon is one of the area\'s premier spots for professional haircare and beauty treatments. Established in 2005 as Mimi Hair and Body Care, the salon operated out of Blooms & Greens Flower Shop, providing both beauty services and flowers to the Jackson area. The popularity of the salon eventually led to the conversion of the space into a full-service salon and in 2011 current owner Shara Buday, a member of the original staff, bought the salon from her sister and rebranded it as Champu Salon. Under Shara\'s visionary ownership Champu has continued to grow into one of Jackson\'s most fashionable salons, offering clientele the latest in hair and beauty trends within the unique mountain locale. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Staff</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Shara Buday, Owner</h3>\r\n<p>As the salon owner and founder of the Champu brand, it is Shara\'s vision and style that define the identity of Champu Salon. With a natural gift for color and a passion for styling, Shara has been helping clients achieve their ideal look since she joined the industry in 2001. After developing her career in Boston for four years Shara moved to Jackson in 2005 to become an original staff member of the salon, then known as Mimi Hair and Body Care. In 2011 Shara bought the salon from her sister and established Champu Salon, with a goal of becoming the area\'s premier provider of haircare and beauty. Today, Shara\'s vision continues to grow the salon and has allowed her to achieve her dream of owning a salon brand that is completely her own, while continuing to provide clients with the excellent service they\'ve come to expect.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Audrey Getter</h3>\r\n<p>Audrey first began developing her skills as a professional in the beauty industry as a makeup artist at Clinique. While attending school at Artistic Beauty College to become a certified cosmetologist, Audrey also had the opportunity to learn as an apprentice under one of Arizona\'s top stylists. Audrey\'s ten years of experience as a stylist at high-end salons in Prescott, AZ, in addition to her certification as Pureology stylist and dedication to continuing education keep her ahead of the latest industry trends. A yoga instructor on the side, Audrey loves to spend her free time reading fashion and style blogs and playing in the beautiful outdoors of Jackson Hole.   </p>\r\n<h3>Jen Jeffers</h3>\r\n<p>Nunc ut tortor fermentum, sollicitudin leo vel, ultrices tortor. Fusce et ornare nisi. Aliquam risus lectus, interdum ac enim quis, eleifend vestibulum eros. Suspendisse volutpat eu metus ac interdum. Nullam egestas orci lacus, quis tristique odio auctor nec. Nulla facilisi. Sed lacus lorem, dignissim sit amet velit a, rhoncus volutpat neque. Mauris convallis libero ut lorem porta, non auctor est ultrices.</p>\r\n<h3>Sarah Duke</h3>\r\n<p>Sarah decided to pursue her dream of becoming a hair stylist in 2011, when she enrolled at Paul Mitchell The School in Denver, CO. Graduating in 2012 as a specialist in cutting and color, Sarah and her husband Tyler moved back to Jackson, where Sarah has been a resident for most of her life. As a true Jackson local, Sarah enjoys many of the outdoor activities the area has to offer with her husband and two dogs, Sophie and Gracie. </p>','The Salon','','publish','open','open','','salon','','','2014-01-11 00:33:54','2014-01-11 00:33:54','',0,'http://champusalonjh.com/?page_id=18',0,'page','',0),(22,1,'2013-10-24 23:15:27','2013-10-24 23:15:27','<div class=\"row-fluid services\">\r\n<div class=\"span6\">\r\n<h2>Hair</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Women\'s Cut ... $45 + up</li>\r\n	<li>Men\'s Cut ... $25 + up</li>\r\n	<li>Kid\'s Cut ... $20 + up</li>\r\n	<li>Shampoo + Blow Dry ... $35 + up</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Nails</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Manicure ... $30</li>\r\n	<li>Pedicure ... $65</li>\r\n	\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"span6\">\r\n<h2>Color</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>One Process ... $55 + up</li>\r\n	<li>Full Foil ... $105 + up</li>\r\n	<li>Partial Foil ... $85 + up</li>\r\n	<li>Last Tint ... $25 + up</li>\r\n<li>Brow Tint ... $20 + up</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Waxing</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Brows/Lip/Chin ... $15 each</li>\r\n	\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Services','','publish','open','open','','services','','','2014-01-02 19:19:41','2014-01-02 19:19:41','',0,'http://champusalonjh.com/?page_id=22',0,'page','',0),(24,1,'2013-10-24 23:15:52','2013-10-24 23:15:52','','Weddings','','publish','open','ope